Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（重启一下）（谢谢）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:00.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不是闹着玩哦 也不是那么难做到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:05.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不试试看怎么知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（开玩笑呢 笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}活着真的很难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}但是也同样美好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}是这样 即使成为了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:20.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}也能继续升级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}持续挑战！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不努力是你的撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}软弱的内心也是（啪啪鞭打）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:32.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}用积极向上的对话来恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}定期存档吧（休息也是必要的）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}那完全就是RPG吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}得好好做才行 得好好笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:44.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}如果手册是这么写的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}吸收其中技巧 调整为理想的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}重新制作一份吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}好！好！好！好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:14.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！这是你的时代！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（未来向你招手）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:22.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}在努力过后大声欢笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}再一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！这是你的时代！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:33.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}保持专注不要停！（大脑过热进行时）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:36.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}横扫大Boss然后通关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:40.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}最后全通游戏吧！（你将无人能敌）
